{
  "stem": "16214.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "The day they left, I walked in to my nursing school counselor, and said, I'm getting out of here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I already had two years of nursing school, which was stupid.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Because I should have just finished, and then not do anything with it, and continue on with further education that I wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But I was so angry at them for making me do it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "That this was my first act of like independence.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I dropped out by myself from the school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And even though I still had like a whole year before I could go to the army or something, so I started working part time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Because the school did not-- it was in the middle of school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "So I couldn't start any other education or anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "So, and I felt that I have to support myself some way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "So I-- I was doing in [INAUDIBLE], basically nursing, you know, helping, you know, people-- private patients, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I would do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I-- I had been engaged already at the time to-- at the age of 17, to my gynecology professor, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And I decided I'm not going to leave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "But soon enough, the army started calling me, and I wanted to be a paratrooper.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "My parents were very upset about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And my mother basically gave me an ultimatum.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "She said, either you come here, you're under age.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And-- or I will go and get you myself and bring you to the United States.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they basically gave me about two weeks or so to get out of there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's what happened, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I had some very interesting happenings, actually, in the nursing school which I would like you-- which I would like to tell you about.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
